0. Please execute following script to fetch OpenVanilla's source code.

     `./init.sh`

1. To compile OpenVanilla modulesï¼Œplease execute
   
     `cd Modules`
     `make`

2. To install, please execute script with INSTALL_PREFIX parameter.
   "INSTALL_PREFIX/lib/openvanilla/" refer to the location for your modules.
      
     `INSTALL_PREFIX=/usr/local/ make install` 

